high_descs: Turn right and walk forward across the room to the bread on the dining table, then turn right and walk to the small black side table to the left of the counter.
Pick up the spoon from the small black side table.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the spoon in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Turn left and walk to the dining table containing the head of lettuce.
Put the spoon on the table, underneath the head of lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned spoon on a dining table.

high_descs: Turn to the right and go across the room. Turn right to locate the small black table.
Pick up the spoon from the left side of the table.
Carry the spoon to the right, and face the sink on the left.
Place the spoon in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the spoon.
Take the spoon and turn to the left and face the white table.
Place the spoon under the lettuce on the table.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a spoon and place it on the table, under lettuce.

high_descs: turn right and move to the shelf
pick up the spoon on the shelf
rinse the spoon on the sink
turn right and move to the white table
place the spoon on the table
anns.task_desc: place a clean spoon on the table
